    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014inside and out, it\u2019s practically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service check. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, clean feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and looked after, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
