    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop as if it just rolled off the assembly line. There are absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats are supple with no signs of wear, and the 'new car' scent still lingers. Every electronic feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, backed by a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships. It has never seen a drop of rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
