    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presented is an impeccable E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically superlative, with a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced rod bearing kit for preventative longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, feeding power through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by fresh bushings and an uncompromised suspension geometry. With zero evidence of thermal cycling fatigue or track-induced stress, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the serious enthusiast.",
